Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二海棠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥正在更衣室里面接受采访
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是20周年纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以前夜祭之前还有粉丝见面会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师兄也真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉丝见面会3点开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始后希望你尽可能坐哥哥旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明和我没有关系 坐旁边可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是一个研究会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我还是他师弟啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一大群陌生人围得水泄不通
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,费神应对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让他对局前不要太紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才想让你坐旁边的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旁边有熟人才比较安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟哥哥在人群前容易紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没怎么 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(934,632)}完全没有\N注意到这点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二海棠 难道你比我更加成熟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你也多少感受一下这样的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早点适应会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后万一遇到这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会因为环境分散注意力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是以后自己参加头衔战的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得这么轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好像理所当然一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在才C1C2啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要挑战头衔战的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这样决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不这样想 怎么做棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二海棠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着二海棠说这话时的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我内心也多少被动摇着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 零
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 3点在会场见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在左顾右盼迷茫的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我同龄的他 已经下定了决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事我一直想和你当面说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的那些奖金和比赛出场费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了生活费以外几乎都汇给我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得这样来回报一直以来的关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用想这些事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的 幸田 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当为他保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正给小孩那么多钱也会被挥霍掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 零不是那种孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 像这个年纪的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有花钱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1228,272)}酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(76,374)}吸烟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(294,626)}奇怪的店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,574)}赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜 好不容易有点小钱却没地方花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只剩女人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把钱全部花在任性的女友身上之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 这个方面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 请去别处玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像会长说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在成年之前我帮你保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用的时候随时说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香子怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像经常去你那里 有没有给你添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有说吗 果然呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经完全不知道她在想什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 姐姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸田八段 桐山五段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉能让我拍张照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 我该说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是父亲如果知道这件事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我就没有能做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到东京都内还有这样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他们一直错过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐也好父亲也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都不想割舍对方的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,宗谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂我说 宗合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看都淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是在旁边的话就带他过来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 你也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就要开始了 主角怎么能在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒吸了一囗气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不到他的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到他身影的那个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界变得悄无声息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的样子没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像时间都停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆中有人在窃窃私语
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他消失的那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长空划破 沉重的雨倾盆而下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和那样的人对局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1130,714)}银之线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(128,298)}水面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他进入会场后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寂静无声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人群分成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真对不起大家 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚刚在庭院里呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠闲地看鲤鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么呀这是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那快开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗谷 上台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十五岁 还是中学生就成为职业棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十一岁 成为取得头衔的最年轻棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次次的刷新将棋界的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史上首次取得了全部的七大头衔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后十数年经过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是继续稳坐在王座之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的身影未曾变过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不褪色 不埋没 一尘不染
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用压倒性的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静静地安坐在那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被比作神明的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有恶魔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定是那样的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 有请岛田八段发言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天虽然是工作日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却有众多棋友到场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿到挑战者资格已经过了三周
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都非常匆忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:43.96,Top,,0,0,0,,前夜祭结束前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛田先生说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两局呐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那怪物对决首先要赢得两局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则的话无法到达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第六局的会馆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:10:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛田开八段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮子王B07比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一局 一百一十四手 认输
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟爸爸说了什么多余的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我在邮件里回复的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么也没有说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不光停了我的信用卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还逼问了一大堆问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说我什么都没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 不都是姐姐你自作自受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作自受？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么居高临下的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为自己是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只会畏畏缩缩的烦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下着有气无力的将棋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这些没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明里姐…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们慢慢谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架了 零…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来来 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零会被欺负了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在看起来有点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女 是魔女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 豆皮寿司我们还是自己吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说可来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零碰上了麻烦的家伙昵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊 那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近的 很照顾我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是这家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一副可怜的样子融入进去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要弄得一团糟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钻入别人的家中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焦躁不安 内心忐忑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到面色惨白的零
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那张未曾见过的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一次都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脸面向这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 吃掉这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和姐姐做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸡蛋和芝麻都放了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很甜 非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了就有精神了 一定要吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么 真让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不是好人 那个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 日向 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦 这样生气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一直一言不发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐也有点这么觉得 只有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点哦 只有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1150,708)}水面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(214,300)}青色的夜空下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆皮太甜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这块还放了切碎的腌芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每块都不一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就根本停不下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃胖了怎么办嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自跟过来又擅自开吃还要抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二层都是蔬菜系？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筑前煮？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像老太婆一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表现得太明显了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我很持家吧」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单身男士对这种类型的都很饥渴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有秋葵和西兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煮过后加上麻油和盐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韩式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 再不回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲做了晚饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裙子好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一吃饱就感觉困了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 借我件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有运动衫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才被爸爸训过吧 快回家呐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚点打个电话过去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别打开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于放松下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 是谁呐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个初中生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是那个人妻吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人妻是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 难道是说明里姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫明里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她抱着的孩子是妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那三人是姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便说下 明里姐的年龄应该跟姐姐你差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那究竟是哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初中生还是那个大妈…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了…怎么就扯上这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个都不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你刚才说了…大妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…难道是那个幼儿园的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这变态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.47,Top,,0,0,0,,你倒是快点回家啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 我在零这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在零这里的话就没意见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也已经没电车了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 为什么就不相信自己女儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经搞不懂香子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真合得来呢 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你之后有什么打算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸很担心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸总是搞不清状况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么「既然人家那么照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把男朋友带回来见个面」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我足足大了二十岁 有家室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更别说还是爸爸的师弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能带回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会选择那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小不点 竟然说我是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要真是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会像现在这样丢人又辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 零 我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机微弱的光线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一次次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微微映照出她的轮廓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是静静看着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个房间被染成了青蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二人在深深的水下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一味下沉般的午夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说了声「再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想回一句嗯 却又咽了回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 我怀着破碎的心离开了那个家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依旧如此 亳无改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无力改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法成为姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没能变成陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 你跑过来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 值日打扫花了些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值日打扫…好久没听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个词真让人怀念呐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 你真的还是个学生呐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始二海堂等你都等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你来了 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢了哦 最后一局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 我下赛季就跟你一样是C1了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外态度也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼 重田选手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留级确定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还真是心跳加速呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差点以为你就要跟我一个级别了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思 你在哪里看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪个将棋界的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这赛季我可是游刃有余
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有坏消息就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这赛季也确定A级保级成功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 该说命悬一线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.82,0:22:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是千钧一发程度的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千钧一发吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话从师兄口里说出来就更沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 恭喜你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两都捂着眼角
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于追上你了 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待跟你直接对决呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.59,0:22:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 对手哟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说着的二海堂的神情太过耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我微闭双目
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睑处又浮现出今早河边的一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:15.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}川沿いを走る電車の音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}うつむいて咲く向日葵の色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:22.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}夕焼けがしましまのボーダーになる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:26.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}『ありがとう』って君がいうたんび
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:30.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}泣きそうな気持ちになるのはなんでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}子供みたいにさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:41.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}涙なら冷蔵庫に置いてきたはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:44.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}勝ってうれしいはないちもんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}あの娘が欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:49.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}さよならバイスタンダー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}僕らは歩いて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.43,0:00:55.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}この道行きの最後が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}天国かそこらじゃあないとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:04.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}ただの君と笑って立っていたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}誇らしさとか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:07.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}願いとか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:11.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}希望とかもっとずっと持ち合わせとくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:17.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}こわくて　こわくて　こわくて　沈みそうでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:23.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}守るよ　守るよ　ぼくの全てを捧げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:26.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}目の前の君に誓うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:15.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}沿着河边开过的电车的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}俯下头绽放的向日葵的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:22.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}晚霞化为一条条的纹样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:26.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}你每次说谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:30.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}为什么都会感觉想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}像个孩子似的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:41.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}泪水应该已经留在冰箱里了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:44.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}赢了好开心 笑容如花绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}想要献给那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:49.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}再见了旁观者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}我们要前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.43,0:00:55.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}哪怕这条道路的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}不是什么天国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:04.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}我只想和真实的你笑着站在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}自豪什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:07.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}愿望什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:11.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}希望什么的早就填满了心里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:17.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}好怕 好怕 好怕 像要沉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:23.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}守护 守护 守护你 献上我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:26.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}对眼前的你发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1070,710)}青色的夜空下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下个月就要18岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比常人晚一年升上高二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依旧什么都不能改变的
